<TEXT>
   American Telephone &amp; Telegraph Co. has unveiled
four personal computers made to AT&amp;T specifications by Intel Corp.,
which is substantially replacing Italy's Ing. C. Olivetti &amp; Co. as
the company's PC supplier.
